Package: hexkart
Type: Package
Title: hexkart: Kart simulation for model training
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Javier Luraschi
Maintainer: Javier Luraschi <javier@rstudio.com>
Description: Provides tools to render and capture kart training data using
  'HTML'  widgets  and 'Shiny' applications. It can be used to: Collect kart
  playing styles, create test cases for image classification and render trained
  models over an interactive kart simulation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
  R (>= 3.1.2)
Imports:
  htmlwidgets,
  shiny,
  miniUI
Suggests:
  testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
